<template><div><h1 id="exercicio-heranca-classes-abstratas-e-interface" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#exercicio-heranca-classes-abstratas-e-interface"><span>Exercício Herança classes Abstratas e Interface</span></a></h1>
